---
// services/cosmetic-dentistry.astro (continued)
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Cosmetic Dentistry | Dr. Yukti Ghei Gupta Dental Clinic">
    <div class="relative min-h-screen">
        <!-- Background Image -->
        <div class="absolute inset-0 z-0">
            <img
                src="/background.svg"
                alt="Background Pattern"
                class="w-full h-full object-cover"
            />
        </div>

        <!-- Content Container -->
        <div class="relative z-10 container mx-auto mt-10 px-4 py-16">
            <!-- Hero Section -->
            <section class="mb-16">
                <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center">
                    <div class="md:w-1/2 mb-8 md:mb-0 md:pr-8">
                        <h1
                            class="text-5xl font-bold mb-6 bg-clip-text text-transparent bg-gradient-to-r from-indigo-500 to-purple-600"
                        >
                            Cosmetic Dentistry
                        </h1>
                        <p class="text-xl text-gray-700">
                            Transform your smile and boost your confidence with
                            our advanced cosmetic dental procedures
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>

            <!-- Main Content -->
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-12">
                <!-- Detailed Description -->
                <div class="lg:col-span-2">
                    <div
                        class="bg-white bg-opacity-90 rounded-xl shadow-xl p-8 mb-8"
                    >
                        <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold mb-6 text-indigo-600">
                            Transform Your Smile
                        </h2>

                        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">
                            At Dr. Yukti Ghei Gupta's Dental Clinic, our
                            cosmetic dentistry services are designed to enhance
                            the appearance of your smile while maintaining
                            optimal oral health. We understand that a beautiful
                            smile can significantly impact your self-confidence
                            and quality of life. Our comprehensive approach to
                            cosmetic dentistry combines artistic vision with
                            advanced dental techniques to create stunning,
                            natural-looking results that complement your facial
                            features and personality.
                        </p>

                        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">
                            Dr. Yukti Ghei Gupta brings extensive training and
                            expertise in cosmetic dentistry to every procedure.
                            Her meticulous attention to detail and commitment to
                            aesthetic excellence ensures that each patient
                            receives personalized care tailored to their unique
                            dental needs and cosmetic goals. Using
                            state-of-the-art technology and premium materials,
                            we deliver exceptional results that not only look
                            beautiful but also function properly and stand the
                            test of time.
                        </p>

                        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">
                            Our cosmetic dentistry journey begins with a
                            thorough consultation where Dr. Yukti takes the time
                            to understand your aesthetic concerns and desires.
                            Through digital imaging and smile design technology,
                            we can show you a preview of your potential results
                            before any treatment begins. This collaborative
                            approach allows you to actively participate in
                            designing your dream smile, ensuring your complete
                            satisfaction with the final outcome.
                        </p>

                        <h3 class="text-2xl font-medium mb-4 text-purple-600">
                            The Science Behind Your Smile
                        </h3>

                        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">
                            Cosmetic dentistry is a perfect blend of science and
                            art. Beyond the aesthetic improvements, many
                            cosmetic procedures also contribute to better oral
                            health. For instance, straightening misaligned teeth
                            can improve bite function and reduce the risk of
                            tooth decay and gum disease. Similarly, replacing
                            missing teeth with dental implants or bridges
                            prevents remaining teeth from shifting and preserves
                            facial structure.
                        </p>

                        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">
                            At our clinic, we leverage the latest advancements
                            in dental materials and techniques to achieve
                            results that were not possible just a few years ago.
                            Today's cosmetic materials, such as porcelain
                            veneers and composite resins, closely mimic the
                            translucency and texture of natural teeth, making
                            cosmetic restorations virtually indistinguishable
                            from your natural teeth. These materials are also
                            more durable and stain-resistant than ever before,
                            ensuring that your new smile remains beautiful for
                            years to come.
                        </p>

                        <p class="text-gray-700">
                            Our commitment to continuing education means that
                            Dr. Yukti and our team stay at the forefront of
                            cosmetic dentistry innovations. We regularly attend
                            advanced training courses and workshops to master
                            new techniques and technologies that can benefit our
                            patients. This dedication to excellence allows us to
                            offer the most effective and minimally invasive
                            cosmetic treatments available in modern dentistry.
                        </p>
                    </div>

                    <div
                        class="bg-white bg-opacity-90 rounded-xl shadow-xl p-8"
                    >
                        <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold mb-6 text-indigo-600">
                            Our Cosmetic Dentistry Procedures
                        </h2>

                        <div class="mb-8">
                            <h3
                                class="text-2xl font-medium mb-4 text-purple-600"
                            >
                                Teeth Whitening
                            </h3>
                            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
                                Our professional teeth whitening treatments can
                                brighten your smile by several shades in just
                                one visit. Unlike over-the-counter products, our
                                in-office whitening uses higher-concentration
                                bleaching agents with special safeguards to
                                protect your gums and tooth enamel. We also
                                offer customized take-home whitening kits for
                                those who prefer to whiten gradually or maintain
                                their results after an in-office treatment.
                            </p>
                            <p class="text-gray-700">
                                The whitening process is completely safe when
                                performed under professional supervision. Dr.
                                Yukti carefully evaluates your oral health
                                before recommending the most suitable whitening
                                option for your specific needs. Our treatments
                                are designed to minimize sensitivity while
                                maximizing results, giving you a brilliantly
                                white smile that looks natural and enhances your
                                overall appearance.
                            </p>
                        </div>

                        <div class="mb-8">
                            <h3
                                class="text-2xl font-medium mb-4 text-purple-600"
                            >
                                Porcelain Veneers
                            </h3>
                            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
                                Veneers are ultra-thin shells of medical-grade
                                ceramic (porcelain) that are bonded to the front
                                surfaces of teeth to improve their appearance.
                                They can correct a wide range of cosmetic
                                concerns, including discoloration, chips,
                                cracks, gaps, minor misalignments, and
                                irregularly shaped teeth. Each veneer is
                                custom-crafted to match the color and
                                translucency of your natural teeth, resulting in
                                a seamless smile transformation.
                            </p>
                            <p class="text-gray-700">
                                The veneer process typically requires two to
                                three visits. During the first appointment, Dr.
                                Yukti will prepare your teeth by removing a
                                small amount of enamel (about 0.5mm) to
                                accommodate the thickness of the veneers.
                                Impressions of your teeth are then taken and
                                sent to a dental laboratory where your custom
                                veneers are fabricated. In the meantime, you'll
                                wear temporary veneers. When your permanent
                                veneers are ready, you'll return to our office
                                for the final fitting and bonding, walking out
                                with a completely transformed smile.
                            </p>
                        </div>

                        <div class="mb-8">
                            <h3
                                class="text-2xl font-medium mb-4 text-purple-600"
                            >
                                Dental Bonding
                            </h3>
                            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
                                Dental bonding is a versatile cosmetic procedure
                                that uses tooth-colored composite resin to
                                repair damaged, discolored, or misshapen teeth.
                                The composite material is applied directly to
                                the tooth surface, sculpted into the desired
                                shape, hardened with a special light, and then
                                polished to match the sheen of your natural
                                teeth. Bonding is an excellent solution for
                                minor cosmetic issues and can be completed in
                                just one visit.
                            </p>
                            <p class="text-gray-700">
                                One of the advantages of dental bonding is that
                                it requires minimal or no removal of tooth
                                enamel, making it a more conservative option
                                compared to veneers. While not as durable or
                                stain-resistant as porcelain restorations,
                                bonding is more affordable and can last several
                                years with proper care. Dr. Yukti's artistic eye
                                and precise technique ensure that bonding
                                results look completely natural and blend
                                seamlessly with your smile.
                            </p>
                        </div>

                        <div>
                            <h3
                                class="text-2xl font-medium mb-4 text-purple-600"
                            >
                                Smile Makeovers
                            </h3>
                            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
                                A smile makeover is a comprehensive treatment
                                plan that combines multiple cosmetic procedures
                                to achieve a complete smile transformation. It
                                may include any combination of teeth whitening,
                                veneers, bonding, crowns, implants, gum
                                contouring, and orthodontics, depending on your
                                specific needs and goals. Each smile makeover is
                                uniquely designed to address all aspects of your
                                smile's appearance while ensuring optimal oral
                                health and function.
                            </p>
                            <p class="text-gray-700">
                                The smile makeover process begins with an
                                in-depth consultation and comprehensive
                                examination of your oral health. Dr. Yukti will
                                discuss your aesthetic goals, evaluate your
                                facial features, and consider factors such as
                                your skin tone, facial symmetry, and personality
                                when designing your ideal smile. Using digital
                                smile design technology, we can show you a
                                preview of your potential results and make
                                adjustments based on your feedback before
                                beginning any treatment.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Sidebar -->
                <div>
                    <div
                        class="bg-white bg-opacity-90 rounded-xl shadow-xl p-8 mb-8 sticky top-20"
                    >
                        <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-6 text-indigo-600">
                            Our Cosmetic Services
                        </h3>

                        <ul class="space-y-4">
                            <li class="flex items-center">
                                <span class="text-purple-600 mr-3">✓</span>
                                <span class="text-gray-700 font-medium"
                                    >Professional Teeth Whitening</span
                                >
                            </li>
                            <li class="flex items-center">
                                <span class="text-purple-600 mr-3">✓</span>
                                <span class="text-gray-700 font-medium"
                                    >Porcelain Veneers</span
                                >
                            </li>
                            <li class="flex items-center">
                                <span class="text-purple-600 mr-3">✓</span>
                                <span class="text-gray-700 font-medium"
                                    >Dental Bonding</span
                                >
                            </li>
                            <li class="flex items-center">
                                <span class="text-purple-600 mr-3">✓</span>
                                <span class="text-gray-700 font-medium"
                                    >Smile Makeovers</span
                                >
                            </li>
                            <li class="flex items-center">
                                <span class="text-purple-600 mr-3">✓</span>
                                <span class="text-gray-700 font-medium"
                                    >Tooth-Colored Fillings</span
                                >
                            </li>
                            <li class="flex items-center">
                                <span class="text-purple-600 mr-3">✓</span>
                                <span class="text-gray-700 font-medium"
                                    >Gum Contouring</span
                                >
                            </li>
                            <li class="flex items-center">
                                <span class="text-purple-600 mr-3">✓</span>
                                <span class="text-gray-700 font-medium"
                                    >Cosmetic Crowns and Bridges</span
                                >
                            </li>
                        </ul>

                        <div class="mt-8">
                            <h4 class="font-medium text-purple-600 mb-2">
                                Ready to transform your smile?
                            </h4>
                            <button
                                onclick="document.getElementById('contactUs').scrollIntoView({ behavior: 'smooth' })"
                                class="w-full px-6 py-3 rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-r from-indigo-500 to-purple-600 text-white font-semibold text-lg shadow-lg transform transition duration-300 ease-in-out hover:scale-105 hover:shadow-xl cursor-pointer"
                            >
                                Book Appointment
                            </button>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div
                        class="bg-white bg-opacity-90 rounded-xl shadow-xl p-8"
                    >
                        <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-6 text-indigo-600">
                            Patient Testimonial
                        </h3>

                        <div
                            class="bg-gradient-to-r from-indigo-50 to-purple-50 p-6 rounded-lg shadow"
                        >
                            <p class="text-gray-700 italic mb-4">
                                "I was always self-conscious about my smile, but
                                after getting porcelain veneers with Dr. Yukti,
                                I can't stop smiling! The process was
                                comfortable, and the results exceeded my
                                expectations. My new smile looks completely
                                natural, and I've received so many compliments.
                                Thank you for changing my life!"
                            </p>
                            <p class="font-medium text-indigo-600">
                                — Priya S., Amritsar
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- FAQ Section -->
            <section
                class="mt-16 bg-white bg-opacity-90 rounded-xl shadow-xl p-8"
            >
                <h2
                    class="text-3xl font-semibold mb-8 text-center text-indigo-600"
                >
                    Frequently Asked Questions
                </h2>

                <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
                    <div>
                        <h3 class="text-xl font-medium mb-3 text-purple-600">
                            How long do cosmetic dental procedures last?
                        </h3>
                        <p class="text-gray-700">
                            The longevity of cosmetic treatments varies
                            depending on the procedure and your oral hygiene
                            habits. Professional teeth whitening can last 1-3
                            years, dental bonding 3-7 years, and porcelain
                            veneers 10-15+ years with proper care. Regular
                            dental check-ups and good oral hygiene can
                            significantly extend the life of your cosmetic
                            treatments.
                        </p>
                    </div>

                    <div>
                        <h3 class="text-xl font-medium mb-3 text-purple-600">
                            Are cosmetic dental procedures painful?
                        </h3>
                        <p class="text-gray-700">
                            Most cosmetic procedures involve minimal discomfort.
                            We use local anesthesia when necessary to ensure
                            your comfort during treatment. Many patients report
                            little to no pain during and after cosmetic
                            procedures. For anxious patients, we offer sedation
                            options to make the experience completely
                            stress-free.
                        </p>
                    </div>

                    <div>
                        <h3 class="text-xl font-medium mb-3 text-purple-600">
                            How much do cosmetic dentistry procedures cost?
                        </h3>
                        <p class="text-gray-700">
                            The cost varies depending on the specific procedures
                            and the extent of treatment needed. During your
                            consultation, we'll provide a detailed treatment
                            plan with associated costs. We offer flexible
                            payment options and financing plans to make cosmetic
                            dentistry accessible to more patients.
                        </p>
                    </div>

                    <div>
                        <h3 class="text-xl font-medium mb-3 text-purple-600">
                            Will my cosmetic dental work look natural?
                        </h3>
                        <p class="text-gray-700">
                            Absolutely! Dr. Yukti specializes in creating
                            natural-looking results that enhance your smile
                            while complementing your facial features. We use
                            high-quality materials that mimic the translucency
                            and texture of natural teeth. Our goal is to create
                            a beautiful smile that looks like it's always been
                            yours.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>
            <!-- CTA Section -->
            <section
                id="contactUs"
                class="mt-16 bg-white bg-opacity-90 rounded-xl shadow-xl p-8"
            >
                <h2
                    class="text-3xl font-semibold mb-8 text-center text-indigo-600"
                >
                    Schedule Your Cosmetic Consultation
                </h2>

                <form class="max-w-2xl mx-auto">
                    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-6">
                        <div>
                            <label class="block text-gray-700 mb-2" for="name"
                                >Full Name</label
                            >
                            <input
                                type="text"
                                id="name"
                                class="w-full px-4 py-2 border border-gray-300 rounded-lg focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-indigo-500"
                            />
                        </div>

                        <div>
                            <label class="block text-gray-700 mb-2" for="phone"
                                >Phone Number</label
                            >
                            <input
                                type="tel"
                                id="phone"
                                class="w-full px-4 py-2 border border-gray-300 rounded-lg focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-indigo-500"
                            />
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="mb-6">
                        <label class="block text-gray-700 mb-2" for="email"
                            >Email Address</label
                        >
                        <input
                            type="email"
                            id="email"
                            class="w-full px-4 py-2 border border-gray-300 rounded-lg focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-indigo-500"
                        />
                    </div>

                    <div class="mb-6">
                        <label class="block text-gray-700 mb-2" for="procedure"
                            >Interested In</label
                        >
                        <select
                            id="procedure"
                            class="w-full px-4 py-2 border border-gray-300 rounded-lg focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-indigo-500"
                        >
                            <option value="">Select a procedure</option>
                            <option value="whitening">Teeth Whitening</option>
                            <option value="veneers">Porcelain Veneers</option>
                            <option value="bonding">Dental Bonding</option>
                            <option value="makeover">Smile Makeover</option>
                            <option value="other">Other</option>
                        </select>
                    </div>

                    <div class="mb-6">
                        <label class="block text-gray-700 mb-2" for="message"
                            >Additional Information</label
                        >
                        <textarea
                            id="message"
                            rows="4"
                            class="w-full px-4 py-2 border border-gray-300 rounded-lg focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-indigo-500"
                        ></textarea>
                    </div>

                    <button
                        type="submit"
                        class="px-6 py-3 rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-r from-indigo-500 to-purple-600 text-white font-semibold text-lg shadow-lg transform transition duration-300 ease-in-out hover:scale-105 hover:shadow-xl w-full"
                    >
                        Request Consultation
                    </button>
                </form>
            </section>
        </div>

        <script>
            // Any client-side JavaScript can go here
            document.addEventListener("DOMContentLoaded", () => {
                const form = document.querySelector("form");
                if (form) {
                    form.addEventListener("submit", (e) => {
                        e.preventDefault();
                        // Here you would typically handle the form submission
                        alert(
                            "Thank you for your interest in our cosmetic dental services! We will contact you shortly to schedule your consultation.",
                        );
                    });
                }
            });
        </script>
    </div></Layout
>
